"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/533602","Department of Health","false","2016-07-12","<p>The Government expects to publish the review it commissioned on the independently chaired Accelerated Access Review shortly. The Review team are currently considering publication dates.</p>","Mid Norfolk","George Freeman",,"2016-07-12T13:50:42.57Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/533602/answer","Biography information for George Freeman","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/533602/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/533602/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2016-07-07","Innovative Medicines and Medical Technology Review","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, when his Department plans to publish the final Accelerated Access Review related to drug development and innovation; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Sir Charles Walker","Broxbourne","Mr Charles Walker","42142"
